<p itemprop="description">Leadership and guidance involves providing direction, support, and strategic vision to teams and organizations while fostering professional development and driving positive change.</p>

<div class="proficiency-levels">
    <h2>Proficiency Levels</h2>

    <ol class="skill-levels">
        <li>
            <h3>Awareness</h3>
            <p>You can understand different leadership styles and approaches, and recognise the importance of guidance and mentorship in professional development.</p>
        </li>
        <li>
            <h3>Working</h3>
            <p>You can provide guidance to junior colleagues, lead small teams or projects, and demonstrate leadership behaviors in your day-to-day work.</p>
        </li>
        <li>
            <h3>Practitioner</h3>
            <p>You can lead teams and departments effectively, provide strategic guidance, develop others' capabilities, and drive organizational change initiatives.</p>
        </li>
        <li>
            <h3>Expert</h3>
            <p>You can provide senior executive leadership, shape organizational culture and values, influence government policy, and drive transformation across multiple organizations.</p>
        </li>
    </ol>
</div>

